# Vulcan Forge Wallpapers

## Current Wallpapers

### vulcan-forge.png

- **Source:** VulcanOS Project (branding/wallpapers/vulcan-gradient.png)
- **License:** VulcanOS Project License (GPL-compatible)
- **Resolution:** 3840x2160 (4K)
- **Created:** 2024-12-12
- **Author:** VulcanOS Project

## About This Wallpaper

This wallpaper is the original VulcanOS gradient design, created specifically
for the VulcanOS project. It features ember-orange accent colors on a dark
background, embodying the project's "forge" aesthetic.

The wallpaper was generated as part of the VulcanOS branding assets and is
included in the dotfiles for use with the Vulcan Forge theme.

