## Recommended Sources

For custom Vulcan Forge wallpapers:
- Create abstract volcanic/forge imagery with ember accents (#ff6b35)
- Use dark backgrounds (#1a1a1a, #141414)
- Minimalist geometric patterns work well with this theme

## Usage

This wallpaper is included in VulcanOS as the default for the Vulcan Forge theme.
Redistribution must maintain attribution to the VulcanOS project.
